<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>CSS</title>
    <style>
      .container {
        display: grid;
        grid-gap: 5px;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 3fr 1fr;
        grid-template-rows: 100px minmax(min-content, max-content) 100px 100px;
        grid-template-areas: 
        "header header header"
        "left-menu main ad"
        "recommend recommend recommend"
        "footer footer footer";
      }
      .container > * {
        background-color: yellow;
      }
      header {
        grid-area: header;
      }
      #left_menu_container {
        grid-area: left-menu;
      }
      main {
        grid-area: main;
      }
      #ad {
        grid-area: ad;
      }
      #recommend {
        grid-area: recommend;
      }
      footer {
        grid-area: footer;
      }
    
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <header>
        <p>블로그명: B개발자의 하루</p>
        <p> 메뉴들이 있을거에요.</p>
      </header>
      <div id="left_menu_container">
        <div>왼쪽 메뉴바 입니다.</div>
        <% if(typeof menus !== "undefined") { %>
          <% menus.forEach( (menu, index) => { %>
            <div class="items"><%= menu.name %></div>
          <% }) %>
        <% } %>
      </div>
      <main>
        <div id="main">메인은 글을 넣어주자</div>
        <div id="main">글 제목</div>
        <div id="main">글 내용</div>
        <div id="main">댓글</div>
      </main>
      
      
      <div id="ad">
        구글님 광고 자리
      </div>
      
      <div id="recommend">
        <div>추천 게시글</div>
      </div>


      <footer>푸터: 오늘 커밋했니?</footer>
    </div>



    
    
  </body>
</html>
